title: The Atlantic Division is CRAZY (Ft. Colin Blackwell)
description:
Linda and Emily sit down with one of the most recent additions to the Toronto Maple Leafs, Colin Blackwell, who talks about his excitement for the playoffs, playing in Boston wearing a Leafs jersey, and more! Then, ESPN's Kevin Weekes joins us for our 5 Minute Major to talk Top 5 Goalies in the League Today.
